      {
        "id": "05de07cbbf7380cb336189f22d803b0a1a754741",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 477,
          "name": "Jorge Hernandez",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "jorge.hernandez-herrero@att.com",
          "username": "jhh"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-10-31 20:37:27.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThe other changes in the *.properties and *.json files are not necessary and should be working same as in R0 where we have these scripts converting to the right version from $POLICY_HOME/etc/build.info.   \n\nSee:  https://git.onap.org/policy/docker/tree/config/pe/brmsgw-tweaks.sh\n\nNow, the problem is that the $POLICY_HOME/etc/build.info is not generated anymore in policy/engine build so it is not available at runtime.   This is a bug that has been introduced in R1, and was working OK in R0.\n\nThe culprit seems to be related to these changes.   Note the unix_pe_version profile in R0:\n\nhttps://git.onap.org/policy/engine/tree/packages/base/pom.xml?h=release-1.0.0\n\ncompare it with the 1.1.0 version which has been deleted most of it.\n\nhttps://git.onap.org/policy/engine/tree/packages/base/pom.xml",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "0418139bf1b662542fb8529949fb1f4318405213",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 477,
          "name": "Jorge Hernandez",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "jorge.hernandez-herrero@att.com",
          "username": "jhh"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-10-31 20:40:35.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nBottomline, these are the changes that should be done:\n\n1. use project.version instead of commons.version (see pdp-d counterpart review for reference).\n\n2. restore the $POLICY_HOME/etc/build.info generation that was removed from pom files.\n\n3. undo the changes in *.properties, *.json (and .csv) since the docker tweaks scripts should take care of setting the right version.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
